data.description: WOW! Updated 4 bedroom home is located in the desirable neighborhood of Cypresswood. The single story floor plan with the large detached garage and nice backyard is a great balance of form and function.  Many conversation zones in this home including the formal living and family rooms, the dining room and eat in kitchen. Upscale finishes throughout. The primary suite was remodeled to include a luxury bath with a separate shower and soaking tub. Three additional bedrooms, a second full bath plus a half bath, this one has it all! The backyard is a great space to enjoy the outdoors, from the deck to the newly sodded backyard, there’s plenty of space for family gatherings and pets. This place is ready for you!  Just move in and enjoy!  This one checks all the boxes!  Reach out today for a private showing!
